tweet_text:
@AnnoyedOBrien I have a lovely recipe for Mash & Chips right here, Chief.

500g of Tamarian Voles
500g of Bismuth

1) Chip the bismuth into chips.
2) Mash the volesinto a, well, mash.
3) Cook mash in a forge at 1600C for thirty minutes.
3) Sprinkle bismuth chips on mash.

A delicacy on Tamaria.
